data.description: Great Beachside Gated Community. 3 Bedroom 2 ½ Bath Spectacular Townhome in Oceanside Village, with a Detached Garage. Large Eat-In Kitchen, with breakfast bar, beautiful 42” Cherry Cabinets and Brand New Appliances, including: Refrigerator, Smooth Top Range, Microwave and Dishwasher. New Carpet and Vinyl. New Exterior Air Conditioning Unit. All 3 Bedrooms situated upstairs with Living areas on the ground floor with an inside utility room. Glass sliding doors lead to your Private Screened Porch. Two blocks to the beach. Community Amenities include: Pool, Tennis Courts, Basketball Court & Clubhouse. Close to shopping, restaurants, and major roadways.
data.whatILove: Walking Distance to the Ocean and Beachside Park!
